{
  "texts": [
    "Next, we will investigate behavioural changes using Fig. 3c.",
    "The graphs depict how the tweeting behaviour of the active users changes throughout the study period, when controlling for the user turnover (sample effects).",
    "Starting with RU, we notice that users are tweeting less and less over time.",
    "From January 2020 to November 2021, users tweet 49% less in RU due to behavioural changes.",
    "Subsequently, we see a small rise with the outbreak of the war (+5%), followed up by an even steeper decline (-24%)."
  ]
}